{"tid":298501,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"尖咀商場勁刻薄！規定清潔工人唔准飲水","createTime":"2017-06-26T10:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T23:18:04.000Z","uid":55198,"like":118,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fb00ae6b8ca9437460363bb42ad332787ef19e79","tid":298501,"uid":55198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T10:46:17.000Z","msg":"香港地打工仔往往慘過做奴隸，最近有網民講出一個喺尖沙咀某商場女廁遇到嘅親身經歷，竟然有商場管理層，喺強迫清潔姐姐向每個用完廁所嘅人客講「再見」之餘，但又唔俾佢哋飲水，搞到姐姐聲都沙埋，仲要向客人講「唔好意思，我好口乾，同唔到你哋每一個講再見」。究竟邊間商場咁衰？跳轉有更多詳情。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇下網民喺 Maysum 嘅親身經歷：<br />\n========================================<br />\n我想講呢件事出來，唔係要搏咩。但我既fb有不少有關方面既高層。我好希望佢地見到，然後可以檢討下呢件事！事緣今日係尖沙咀某大商場如廁。<br />\n<br />\n有個清潔姐姐聲都沙晒，都要頂住同我講&quot;唔好意思，我好口乾，同唔到你地每一個人講再見&quot;我好驚訝地又天真地問&quot;咁仲唔飲水？&quot;點知阿姐話，公司規定，工作時唔可以飲水，就算帶係身邊，收入廁所，都唔比！一發現左就會掉！聽完真係好嬲！會唔會太唔人道呀？你要d阿姐同每一個如廁後既人講再見，但講足一日都唔比飲水！原來佢地就算無野抹，個身體都要郁，因為企定定的話會比人話！如果比人影左相就會投訴去上面！<br />\n<br />\n總之工作咁多個鐘，就要不飲水不休息地做！！將心彼己丫，你兩個鐘唔飲水都辛苦啦！何況一個咁努力維持廁所清潔既員工！！！<br />\n<br />\n其實， 清潔阿姐都係人，都有需要，好應該整個休息室比佢地，隔一段時間休息下，唔係全日係個廁所，咁多細菌既地方standby! 亦絕對唔應該限制佢地有飲水既人權！！邊間商場我唔講啦，唔好影響阿姐(我真係不能開名，以保護阿姐，sorry)。而我亦相信唔係一間半間既問題！我見過阿姐食lunch要係廁所食！！其實我地每一個人都唔應該要係廁所休息同食飯！<br />\n<br />\n商場又好，公廁又好，可唔可以拎番d人性出來對自己既員工？！<br />\n<br />\n最後買左枝水比阿姐，叫佢拿拿林飲左佢快手掉埋佢，阿姐好瘦好瘦&hellip;&hellip;我記得佢講左句&ldquo; 而家搵食好難架&rdquo; 我好希望一個人既努力有回報，至少能得到尊重！<br />\n========================================<br />\n<br />\n其實細個老師就已經有教，每個人每日要飲 8 杯水，而家開工幾粒鐘體力勞動，仲要 Keep 住講嘢，但就唔俾飲水，真係同做奴隸冇乜分別。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.eprice.com.hk/fun/talk/18/7962/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.eprice.com.hk%2Ffun%2Ftalk%2F18%2F7962%2F&d=kflC9PVWCPKvjn1plzwuSQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=14e18556\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.eprice.com.hk/fun/talk/18/7962/</a>"},{"pid":"c23b4212194d7405253b16f33907dc7fa7672029","tid":298501,"uid":55198,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T10:51:22.000Z","msg":"「搵食艱難」這句說話，放在一些高齡兼低技術的員工身上顯得非常貼切，他們大多從事厭惡性行業，賺取極低微的薪金，此外，還要面對僱主極苛刻的要求。最近就有一名化妝師於網上指，尖沙咀某商場除了要求清潔廁所的員工需要向顧客打招呼外，更不准他們於工作期間飲水，被批刻薄。<br />\n<br />\n化妝師「 Maysum 」於個人 Facebook 專頁上發文，指昨日到尖沙咀某大商場如廁時，見到一位清潔姐姐用沙啞的聲線向她說：「唔好意思，我好口乾，同唔到你地每一個人講再見。」細問下之發現，該公司除了要求清潔廁所的員工需要向顧客打招呼外，更不能於工作時飲水，一經發現水樽將會被掉，此外，公司又要求員工即使無事可做，身體都要有所動作，否則會被人認為「太空閒」。<br />\n<br />\nMaysum 批評有關指引極不人道，指商場又好，公廁又好，都應該拿出人性對待自己的員工，她最後買了一枝水給那位清潔姐姐，著對方飲水。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員鄺俊宇亦於該貼文上留言，質疑涉事商場已經觸犯《職業安全及健康規例》當中的「須向僱員提供足夠的飲用水」條文，並正在跟進事件。"},{"pid":"24eaf8f8f31fc75c36ecdfdd27b858d6921662c2","tid":298501,"uid":26721,"like":5,"dislike":20,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T11:03:40.000Z","msg":"飲左都唔撚知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁重奴性 咁聽話？"},{"pid":"1c92e4f7811b0009e6077a57b9d7e8aae1c997a8","tid":298501,"uid":54060,"like":20,"dislike":9,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:32:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飲左都唔撚知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁重奴性 咁聽話？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係想話阿姐<br />\n不過佢奴性真係太重"},{"pid":"5a2e5afde85cb1184fbbba3e31d70af1dca6ea44","tid":298501,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4a746f57cc03d2e3cffb2c3579678cf66537948","tid":298501,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:37:26.000Z","msg":"真係痴撚線"},{"pid":"744457efe1d687037671845cb5717992f3d99a6d","tid":298501,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:38:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>飲左都唔撚知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁重奴性 咁聽話？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係想話阿姐<br />\n不過佢奴性真係太重</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n突擊檢查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"293f067a9fe21fe375b2ca9cdde31889556e88d5","tid":298501,"uid":39195,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:38:44.000Z","msg":"邊個mall ? 永久blacklist<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3272f2f67c9d877fda918a29b484d0369ca5b04","tid":298501,"uid":9769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:40:21.000Z","msg":"聽講係海港城（好似係）"},{"pid":"4ae9a036b5567ff0a394482241bb99fde9a1fd5d","tid":298501,"uid":53223,"like":90,"dislike":0,"score":90,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:48:00.000Z","msg":"斯文敗類，衣冠禽獸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話阿姐奴性重的人，人哋唔係18 22，除時做咩都得。<br />\n<br />\n反而D高層都叫讀過書，仲咁做簡直毫無廉恥，根本就故意蝦人哋，狗都不如。"},{"pid":"90f92b12d2da8414c7f59f4bb49afd5b245b638c","tid":298501,"uid":55198,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:54:43.000Z","msg":"推到個商場仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c8731aa4089640b53f0e986add77da2be446f8","tid":298501,"uid":39195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T04:30:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽講係海港城（好似係）</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b334e933b1a714b691feb592ad1b5fa8d16c6ad1","tid":298501,"uid":124277,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T04:34:53.000Z","msg":"人工包埋架啦<br />\n又無人迫你做"},{"pid":"debe588b47cf8e08e20c56fdf90487ed5843d148","tid":298501,"uid":37413,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T04:41:37.000Z","msg":"戇鳩飲水係人類生理需要<br />\n冇水飲仲辛苦過冇飯食"},{"pid":"1ea9e245b677c622e374c3ade671f8451762b418","tid":298501,"uid":799,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T04:42:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飲左都唔撚知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁重奴性 咁聽話？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢有心裝鳩你隨時炒得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fb097dedc8abed8ccc5b05e95689c224b9a5da6","tid":298501,"uid":19979,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T04:45:43.000Z","msg":"屌老母 去個廁所都要講再見<br />\n日日去果到痾屎啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9079d29b672828a37cd9aa6e76e0c8573904e99b","tid":298501,"uid":74145,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T04:48:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>飲左都唔撚知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咁重奴性 咁聽話？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係想話阿姐<br />\n不過佢奴性真係太重</blockquote><br />\n大佬，飲水日日都需要，長期偷飲你估會唔會比人發現，發現左個呀姐比人炒埋攞咩養家？奴性重真係個環境逼出黎，如果佢比人炒左，有咩地方可以幫佢拎番應有權益？"},{"pid":"f44182957fde110110f7784ef32700e3f9d7197c","tid":298501,"uid":60635,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T04:49:40.000Z","msg":"比人捉到，肯定話只係叫你唔好係客面前飲水，員工誤解左。<br />\n<br />\n實情係要你一朝到晚都係客面前，姐係唔比飲。大家都係打工，好心D 經理咪咁痴線啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd22e855655eefe84503a63fb0d1750c9c18534","tid":298501,"uid":106375,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T04:50:06.000Z","msg":"On9先諗得出呢啲規矩<br />\n邊有人想痾完屎出黎見到有人同自己打招呼"},{"pid":"b9abf5e2d21973603d31bcf53271afc2e8722ad5","tid":298501,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T04:51:44.000Z","msg":"雖然唔飲水好閒,但都無理由剝削人地飲水既權利啫<br />\n利申:每日液體攝取量唔過1L"},{"pid":"f080420f63101cb691c03b7b2822c3ddac1f1e9d","tid":298501,"uid":58998,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T04:52:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>On9先諗得出呢啲規矩<br />\n邊有人想痾完屎出黎見到有人同自己打招呼</blockquote><br />\n小姐，又黎痾呀？多謝光臨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3300540b0442600a4347b3b06d7b0f0de633d3f","tid":298501,"uid":43285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T04:53:50.000Z","msg":"應該係H&amp;M上面個個 咁多個TST商場得個個會有人講再見"},{"pid":"20a956c546eee05ad0a1f0d52634cc2e539484da","tid":298501,"uid":71738,"like":0,"dislike":